{"word":"ἐπιπολάζω","slug":"ἐπιπολάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιπολάζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐπιπολή'><el>ἐπιπολή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to come to the surface, float</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to be uppermost, to be prevalent</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to be forward;</i> <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to behave insolently to</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to be engaged upon</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}